Conférences internationales

   Note : Il s’agit de présentations orales, sauf lorsque la mention
   « poster » est précisée.
   « The identity of dispositions » (Barton, A., Grenier, O., Jansen, L.,
   & Ethier, J.-F.), 10th International Conference on Formal Ontology in
   Information Science (FOIS 2018), Le Cap, Afrique du Sud, 21/09/2018
   « First steps towards an ontology of belief » (Barton, A., Duncan, W.,
   Toyoshima, F. & Ethier, J.-F.), 2nd International Workshop on
   Epistemology in Ontologies (EPINON), Joint Ontology Workshops (JOWO
   2018), Le Cap, Afrique du Sud, 17/09/2018
   « The identity and mereology of pathological dispositions » (Barton,
   A., Grenier, O., & Ethier, J.-F.), 9th International Conference on
   Biomedical Ontology (ICBO 2018), Corvallis, Oregon, Etats-Unis,
   08/08/2018
   « Consent to participation to research activities in a Learning Health
   System: A scoping review » (Barton, A., Cumyn, A., Jalbert, R., Dault,
   R. & Ethier, J.-F.) (poster), 2nd annual symposium on the ethical,
   legal and social implications of learning health systems (ELSI-LHS),
   Ann Arbor, Etats-Unis, 15/11/2017
   « Ambiguities in medical bitemporalized relational databases: A
   referent tracking view » (Barton, A., Khnaisser, C., Lavoie, L. &
   Ethier, J.-F.), The Foundational Stance (FOUST, JOWO-2017), Bolzano,
   Italie, 22/09/2017
   « A taxonomy of disposition-parthood » (Barton, A., Jansen, L. &
   Ethier, J.-F.), Ontology and data in Life Sciences (ODLS, JOWO-2017),
   Bolzano, Italie, 21/09/2017
   « What is a risk? A formal representation of risk of stroke for people
   with atrial fibrillation. 8th International Conference on Biomedical
   Ontology (ICBO 2017), (Barton, A., Jansen, L. & Ethier, J.-F.),
   Newcastle, Angleterre, 15/09/2017
   « Ontologies to support Learning Health Systems » (Barton, A., Ethier,
   J.-F., & Taseen, R.), Clinical Terminology Shock & Awe, 5th Annual
   Workshop of the Clinical and Translational Science Ontology Group,
   Buffalo, Etats-Unis (New York), 08/09/2016
   « Improving the semantics of drug prescription with a realist ontology
   », (Ethier, J.-F., Taseen, R., Lavoie, L. & Barton, A.), International
   Conference on Biomedical Ontologies (ICBO 2016), Corvallis, Etats-Unis
   (Oregon), 03/08/2016
   « On prescribing drug prescriptions », (Taseen, R., Ethier, J.-F. &
